Package: treeExtension
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Tree Utilities for IQ-TREE Newick Outputs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Your", family = "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "your.email@example.com")
)
Description: Minimal, dependency-free helpers for IQ-TREE newick strings. 
    Currently provides make_binary_iqtree(): converts an unrooted, possibly
    multifurcating tree into a rooted binary tree by splitting the outgroup
    branch length equally between the outgroup and ingroup sides.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
